column6: EMPIRE: ACT I, Part 3 (of 3) Daken has shown in the past that he's willing to do absolutely anything to accomplish his goals, but DYING? That seems a bit extreme. However, impossible as it may seem, there are things in life that you can only accomplish after death. Just ask Wolverine' Parental Advisory '$2.99
